ty:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-none text-xs/relaxed text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-2 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-none *:[img:last-child]:rounded-none group relative overflow-hidden bg-card/60 border-border/30 p-0\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 p-6\"><div class=\"font-display text-5xl text-coral mb-4\">01</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Find the cart</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Look for the wooden cart rolling around the festival, draped in phone cords and disco light. Eight landline phones, all real, all ringing.</p></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-coral/10 blur-2xl transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:bg-coral/30\"></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-none text-xs/relaxed text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-2 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-none *:[img:last-child]:rounded-none group relative overflow-hidden bg-card/60 border-border/30 p-0\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 p-6\"><div class=\"font-display text-5xl text-citrus mb-4\">02</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Pick up</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Grab the receiver. A stranger&#x27;s compliment plays — something someone said out loud because they meant it.</p></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-coral/10 blur-2xl transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:bg-coral/30\"></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-none text-xs/relaxed text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-2 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-none *:[img:last-child]:rounded-none group relative overflow-hidden bg-card/60 border-border/30 p-0\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 p-6\"><div class=\"font-display text-5xl text-mint mb-4\">03</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Record yours</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">After the beep, leave a compliment for whoever picks up next. 30 seconds. Be kind. Be specific.</p></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-coral/10 blur-2xl transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:bg-coral/30\"></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-none text-xs/relaxed text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-2 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-none *:[img:last-child]:rounded-none group relative overflow-hidden bg-card/60 border-border/30 p-0\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 p-6\"><div class=\"font-display text-5xl text-magenta mb-4\">04</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Or leave one here</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Can&#x27;t make it to the cart? Drop a text or audio compliment below. We&#x27;ll pipe it into the rotation.</p></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-coral/10 blur-2xl transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:bg-coral/30\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"w-full overflow-hidden py-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1200 80\" class=\"w-full h-20 scale-y-[-1]\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"cordGrad\" x1=\"0\" x2=\"1\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"oklch(0.72 0.21 22)\"></stop><stop offset=\"50%\" stop-color=\"oklch(0.70 0.28 338)\"></stop><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"oklch(0.89 0.17 92)\"></stop></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M0 40 Q 30 0, 60 40 T 120 40 T 180 40 T 240 40 T 300 40 T 360 40 T 420 40 T 480 40 T 540 40 T 600 40 T 660 40 T 720 40 T 780 40 T 840 40 T 900 40 T 960 40 T 1020 40 T 1080 40 T 1140 40 T 1200 40\" stroke=\"url(#cordGrad)\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl text-center\"><p class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-muted-foreground mb-4\">Total compliments received</p><div class=\"flex justify-center gap-2\"><div class=\"relative flex h-24 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-background/80 font-display text-5xl text-citrus shadow-inner md:h-36 md:w-24 md:text-7xl\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">0</span><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 border-t border-border/15\"></div></div><div class=\"relative flex h-24 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-background/80 font-display text-5xl text-citrus shadow-inner md:h-36 md:w-24 md:text-7xl\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">0</span><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 border-t border-border/15\"></div></div><div class=\"relative flex h-24 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-background/80 font-display text-5xl text-citrus shadow-inner md:h-36 md:w-24 md:text-7xl\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">2</span><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 border-t border-border/15\"></div></div><div class=\"relative flex h-24 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-background/80 font-display text-5xl text-citrus shadow-inner md:h-36 md:w-24 md:text-7xl\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">4</span><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 border-t border-border/15\"></div></div><div class=\"relative flex h-24 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-background/80 font-display text-5xl text-citrus shadow-inner md:h-36 md:w-24 md:text-7xl\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">7</span><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 border-t border-border/15\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mt-6 text-muted-foreground/80\">and counting.</p></div></section><section id=\"submit\" class=\"relative px-6 py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10\"><p class=\"font-mono mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-muted-foreground\">Your turn</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-none text-foreground\">LEAVE ONE</h2><p class=\"mt-4 font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;max-width:36rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\">Kind. Specific. 30 seconds or 500 characters. Gets queued, reviewed, then plays on a real phone at the next festival.</p></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-none py-4 text-xs/relaxed text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-2 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-none *:[img:last-child]:rounded-none w-full bg-card/70 border-border/25 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md\" style=\"width:100%\"><d